    <div class="panel-body">

        <br />

        <div style="margin-bottom:15px; text-align:justify">
            <blockquote>
                <p style="color:darkgreen; font-weight:bold">
                    Welcome to the final step of your admission process.
                </p>

                @*<small>Please confirm your Order Number for Acceptance and School Fees payment below. In case of any discrepancy, report immediately to the appropriate authority. Thereafter click on the <b>Fill Student Form</b> button to fill your form<cite title="Source Title"></cite></small>*@
